    "description": "《猎源》是一款给玩家丰富武器选择的横版 Roguelite 动作游戏，让玩家在无限的轮回中，探索这个由逐帧手绘动画组成的中国风味猎源世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/988c55ef6382bc8355ed47c8553bcf9e.avif?t=1763376128\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><br>从能够招来天火焚噬一切的杨奶五火炮，能够抵挡前方一切伤害的赤狂盾，能够以旋风斩横扫一切的裁决刃-“国肠”，到能够从敌人身上虹吸生命能量的血魔毒牙...<br><br>在这个寻找火源的冒险中，你将选择怎样的组合帮你渡过难关？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《猎源》游戏中，从双手斧、盾刀、双手剑、刀、双刀、飞镖到弓箭，我们为7大武器类型设计了37把不同的武器。为了让丰富玩家们的游戏体验，我们为每一把武器单独设计了专属的技能和强化路线，让游戏中产生出11种不同种类武器的组合以及666种不同组合可能性。<br><br>我们希望通过武器给你带来丰富的战斗体验，并通过丰富的组合可能为你带来各式各样的战术应对不同的关卡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/57937ecb2887160ba675c78ffe25bbba.avif?t=1763376128\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><br>为了让 Roguelite 的感觉更强，我们在游戏中设计了场内外两套天赋系统。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在场外，我们为你提供了8个升级方向，每一次的加点都永久有效，保证经过反反复复历炼后的你能够变得更强。<br><br>而在场内，围绕着你具有各类属性的护身飞刀，陪伴在你身边给你带来各种 Buff 的随从，或者额外的二段跳能力？<br><br>我们设计了124张天赋卡并将会在你每次升级时随机抽取三张供你挑选，带来的海量的组合将让你每一局游戏都拥有不同的体验，感受 Roguelite 游戏的随机魅力<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/e4a51dd25ecb72f3d02ca0ee04d3d27f.avif?t=1763376128\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><br>《猎源》采用了和《茶杯头》相同的逐帧动画制作。<br><br>从人物的挥刀到跳跃，再从线稿手绘到上色成品，不仅仅是团队对于游戏的坚持，也是希望给玩家带来不一样的视觉体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
